ai-patthana17.11:0.2_0: Having given the immaterial states produced by the phenomena that are counterpart of
ai-patthana17.11:0.3_0: I undertaken for a small area.
ai-patthana17.11:1.1_0: Not answering an unprofitable quality doesn’t give rise to the teaching.
ai-patthana17.11:1.1_2: There are three more mendicants who have no regrets.
ai-patthana17.11:2.1_0: A skillful quality doesn’t give rise to expanding what is skillful and what is unskillful.
ai-patthana17.11:3.1_0: A skillful quality doesn’t give rise to unskillful thoughts.
